= Panzerkreuzer

The Reichswehr Ministry is demanding the construction of a new battlecruiser, as part of Germany's rearmament. The coalition partners of SPD are united in support, but within the party itself many call upon Chancellor Müller to reject the proposal as one that is unbeneficial to workers and militaristic.
As for our vote, it has never been up to any doubt...

- @vote_yes: Vote yes, for constructing the battlecruiser.

