Chancellor Müller agrees with the party and the SPD votes against, however, only KPD joins it in its protest. The ship will be built - which is something that pleases the Reichswehr and any German Nationalist, and the relationships between SPD and its coalition partners worsen. There is no doubt this is a very positive development for DNVP.

